title: VA - Nu Reggae - New Rare Tunes With A Reagge Flavor (2007) @320
description:
http://i.imgur.com/UODIm4H.jpg



This compilation of Reggae songs is essential for anyone who is truly into the genre. These artists meticulously blend a range of inspirations and genres into their tracks starting with upbeat melodies and slowly transcending into downtempo rhythms. This is a rare album and contains the best examples of Nu Reggae today.
